name: Ulric_Tagge
content:
Ulric Tagge was a human male who served as Head of Public Relations and Messaging at the Tagge Corporation during the Galactic Civil War. A member of the House of Tagge, he was an older brother of Domina Tagge, who sat at the head of the company.
Ulric Tagge first appeared via imagination in the fifth issue of the 2020 comic series Star Wars: Doctor Aphra . He first appeared in-person and was first identified in the 2021 comic War of the Bounty Hunters â€“ Boushh 1.
